&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership, relationship management, organizational planning and project management skills, in addition to technical knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset and desire for business development.&lt;/li&gt;
